br />\n返屋企煮個蝦仁炒蛋 10鐘內搞得掂 (最快應該5-6分鐘就得)<br />\n到時 飯都應該差不多熟 可以開飯<br />\n<br />\n想食得健康 就去街市買1-2斤菜<br />\n洗定 包好 放入雪櫃<br />\n滾水煮完 加豉油就上得枱食得<br />\n<br />\n想豪華少少 就買雞翼 雞脾 整豉油 鹵水<br />\n<br />\n試過買一樽腐乳 + 超市減價雞扒($5)<br />\n夠食兩餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:49:43.000Z","msg":"巴打好有心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食過出面個D咩叉燒炒蛋飯 加個自家制豉油汁<br />\n我頂佢 成50蚊碟 <br />\n叉燒得個幾塊 炒隻蛋薄到好似塊mask咁<br />\n<br />\n食菜加豉油真係頂唔緊 當自己係草食性動物咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n腐乳好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一磚送到成碗飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:59:21.000Z","msg":"我出去買廿蚊叉燒<br />\n份量夠煮三餐叉燒炒滑蛋<br />\n我唔係廚神 但係炒個叉燒滑蛋<br />\n都叫入得口<br />\n圍返條數 10蚊就一餐<br />\n<br />\n食菜同豉油 係夜晚果餐<br />\n有D肚餓 但又唔想食咁多野<br />\n所以先咁食 不過通常都會配雞胸<br />\n<br />\nBTW 其實食得健康 真係有代價 好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f6783d84ab28fae531d85f68a030efa3134d57","tid":987624,"uid":52053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c784e28de9290eadb91e7b3c4dd02e5e83c43abd","tid":987624,"uid":117608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:58:36.000Z","msg":"南山邨夜晚9蚊一底雞蛋仔/夾餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個星期至少食一次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"依家幾點開？好耐冇食過"},{"pid":"7de5e71d2d4e573e0881d755fe48a89dbb40c1aa","tid":987624,"uid":117608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"87f6783d84ab28fae531d85f68a030efa3134d57","tid":987624,"uid":52053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c784e28de9290eadb91e7b3c4dd02e5e83c43abd","tid":987624,"uid":117608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:5